div.div: Rechargeable 10W CREE T6 LED Spotlight Flashlight Hand Torch Camping Lamp 1000lm

Versatile usage
With the front light and two side lights, this multi-functional light is able to meet your various lighting needs.
You can use it for rescue or camping with the front light.
The light on the left side gives off soft white light that suitable for working, while the light on the right side is a red signal light that would be quite helpful in emergency situations.
Adjustable brightness
The front light has two brightness levels, 1000 lumen and 400 lumen, to meet your different lighting requirements. The front light can last up to 4-5 hours on a single charge.
For the left side light, it has two brightness levels as well, including 130 lumen and 70 lumen. You can adjust its brightness to better suit your mood. The left side light can lasts up to 11-12 hours on a single charge.
Rechargeable & Power bank function
By adopting two qualified lithium-ion batteries of total battery capacity up to 3600mAh, this searchlight can be recharged by USB port, and it takes 5-6 hours to be completed charged.
This rechargeable light can also serve as a power bank for your smartphone or mobile devices in emergency. Please note that the input and output voltage are both 5V.
Strap available
It has a large, comfortable handle as well as the optional, adjustable length shoulder strap, making it pretty handy when you go camping, walking the puppy or carrying an umbrella.
You can also hang it on branches, nails, hooks via the strap, making it much more flexible.
Battery indicator light
It has a row of blue indicator lights, showing you the battery level of the light. You are able to recharge the light timely when the blue indicator lights shows one drop of power left.
Emergency lights
If your area gets lot of thunderstorms and power outages, you won't miss this light. When there is no power due to a storm, you can count on this portable light.

li.span: Sufficient brightness: The CREE T6 LED front light provides you with two brightness levels, 1000lm and 400lm. Irradiation distance is about 500m.
Two side lights: with a 130lm daylight white light on the left side and a red signal light on the right side, which perfectly meets your specific lighting needs.
Rechargeable and power bank: battery capacity up to 3600mAh, charged by USB port, and it can also serve as a power bank for your smartphone or mobile devices in emergency.
Power indicator light: 4 blue LEDs indicate you the battery level of this camping lantern. You can recharge the lantern timely when the indicator ligh drops to only one LED indicating.
Easy to use: large and comfortable handle together with adjustable length shoulder strap, making it pretty handy when you go camping, walking dogs, exploring, searching or carrying an umbrella.
